{"tid":1260270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好似陷入在健身騙案!求助","createTime":"2019-06-26T20:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T13:43:20.000Z","uid":249547,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f53100b456c93bc26311b6bfd14792acd8f02a3d","tid":1260270,"uid":249547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T20:04:14.000Z","msg":"今日比個hihi叫左上工廠大廈果啲健身中心<br />\n一開始條友話幫幫手,趕住放工<br />\n跟住上到去比人渡尻我簽咩簽咩<br />\n然後我已為係可以考慮完再報名參加果啲<br />\n我同返佢講我本來諗住返去考慮完先再搞<br />\n但佢話已經簽左約要攞身份證同銀行卡<br />\n我就直接問佢有無得解約果啲<br />\n佢就話有方法既<br />\n就係證明到自己身上既錢同銀行入面唔夠負擔<br />\n我咁岩交完學費無耐銀行先都唔先下<br />\n比佢睇完我銀包同銀行入面真係無錢就比我走了<br />\n不過佢依家有我住址,身份證,銀行卡編號<br />\n我想問下咁多位巴絲打我會唔會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n<br />\nP. S. 間野好似叫Y station, 佢話係新開鋪<br />\n係九龍灣"},{"pid":"7ec1143d98002fd0b03c5785dc7c0671c985cc79","tid":1260270,"uid":212336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T20:23:36.000Z","msg":"大不了破產啫,幾年後又一條好漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26bc2756d52f854afba6a90f7dc73fadc6310bbd","tid":1260270,"uid":249547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ec1143d98002fd0b03c5785dc7c0671c985cc79","tid":1260270,"uid":212336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T20:23:36.000Z","msg":"大不了破產啫,幾年後又一條好漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T20:28:51.000Z","msg":"我唔想變皮住<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488d451f9121bd20b94f31b2a9368f5dbd61fbe1","tid":1260270,"uid":249547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26bc2756d52f854afba6a90f7dc73fadc6310bbd","tid":1260270,"uid":249547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ec1143d98002fd0b03c5785dc7c0671c985cc79","tid":1260270,"uid":212336,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1